    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's been garage-kept since day one. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
