    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and 50/50 weight distribution. This specimen retains its original 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, showing exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The vacuum-controlled manifold system is fully synchronized, ensuring a seamless transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbochargers. The chassis remains rigid with all-original double-wishbone suspension components and a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential. Every bushing is supple, and the five-speed manual transmission shifts with short-throw precision. This is a non-modified, investment-grade example with a flawless cooling system and intact apex seals, ready for the most discerning purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
