    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The original factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine without a hint of UV exposure, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership according to the manufacturer\u2019s rigorous schedule, with a thick folder of service records to prove its pedigree. Every switch, button, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The undercarriage is exceptionally clean, free of any debris or oxidation. This sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. If you are looking for an uncompromising example that looks and drives like it just left the showroom floor, this is the one.",
      "price": 43950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
