    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a high-revving, linear power delivery. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a proactively reinforced rear subframe and fresh bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, while the factory M-Variable differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system's expansion tank, has been maintained to exacting standards. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, reflecting a climate-controlled history free of the typical subframe fatigue or VANOS rattle associated with lesser examples.",
